sequenceDiagram
    participant frontend
    participant P1 as backend.internal:9000
    participant legacy-service
    participant unknown
    frontend->>P1: GET /api/data
    P1-->>frontend: OK (35ms)
    frontend->>legacy-service: GET /api
    legacy-service-->>frontend: OK (50ms)
    frontend->>unknown: internal-call
    unknown-->>frontend: OK (5ms)